type="local"
addr="jms-00L4">equivalence relation</fr:link> on a set <fr:tex>A</fr:tex>, and let <fr:tex>q \colon  A \to  A/E</fr:tex> be the <fr:em>quotient function</fr:em> that sends <fr:tex>a \in  A</fr:tex> to its equivalence class <fr:tex>{ \mathopen {} \left  [ a \right  ] \mathclose {}} _{ E }</fr:tex>. Then <fr:tex>q \colon  A \to  A/E</fr:tex> is <fr:link
href="jms-00M8.xml"
